            <li><a href="/blog/water-coming-through-basement-floor" class="text-sm text-slate-600 hover:text-cyan-600 transition-colors">Floor Seepage</a></li>
            <li><a href="/blog/white-powder-on-basement-walls" class="text-sm text-slate-600 hover:text-cyan-600 transition-colors">Efflorescence</a></li>
